5000|$|Nizamuddin Markaz Masjid or [...] Banglewali Masjid is {{a mosque}} located in Nizamuddin West in South Delhi, India. It was the global {{center for the}} Tablighi network and {{the origin of the}} Tablighi Jamaat. The <b>Tabligh</b> of India was {{primarily}} based here and it was the place of the annual gathering of the <b>Tabligh</b> workers worldwide.It is the birthplace and the headquarters for Tablighi Jammat (An Islamic religious movement based on the principle of the [...] "Work of the Prophets" [...] where the people are accompanied by scholars to come to this pious place, pray and preach the teachings of the Allah and his disciples.|$|E
